description.displayText:
Lena worked for me for a year and is the rare person who has the skills, ability and interest to do both child care and housekeeping and to do it well. Elena was responsible to care
for my 3 children ages 2-7 in the morning, getting them ready,
feeding them breakfast and taking them to school. While they were in school, she took care of the house, cleaned, organized and did laundry until my children got out of school at 2:30. She picked them up and took care of them until 6:00/6:30 in the evening. Elena was focused on the children when she was with them, playing with them, reading to them, coloring with them and taking them to the park. She is extremely conscientious, safe and responsible and was excellent with my children. She was gentle, warm and affectionate. She is reliable, honest, intelligent and has an exceptional character and I recommend her highly.

